  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">START FUND Emergency Response to Burkina Faso Flood 2016 RMARP</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SAFETY NETS: Unconditional cash grant for social protection. The cash will be distributed to women and mothers who are most vulnerable or head households.
CAPACITY BUILDING: Capacity building of project staff on humanitarian fairs and cash programming.
WASH component</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The success of our response will be measured by the number of people who will receive as rapid as possible life-saving emergency assistance according to their basic and priority needs within a month.</narrative>
  </description>
